> @pranavnateri have you seen/tried the option exposed in [this PR](https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-provider-helm/pull/1012)? It specifically mentions slowness due to excessive CRDs from Crossplane, but may be worth trying even if it's not your specific issue. I'll be trying this option out as well.

Thank you! This solved it for us. We do have crospslane and many other CRD-s. Tested with provider 2.11.0.
```    
provider "helm" {
  burst_limit = 300
  kubernetes {
  ...
  }
}
```

